      "status": "Two onboarding doors implemented (web Twilio Verify + pre-verified text-in). Supabase tables applied to project vgedowiwvwfpjymouito. Real provisioning requires configured Twilio, Supabase service role, CLAIM_LINK_SECRET, and Hermes provision hook secrets",
